<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />You sell your people for nothing;</para>

<para style="q1">you have not increased your wealth by doing so.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />You make us a rebuke to our neighbors,</para>

<para style="q1">scoffed and mocked by those around us.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />You make us an insult among the nations,</para>

<para style="q1">a shaking of the head among the peoples.</para>
